dc.title: United States Chemical Weapons Convention Web Site
dc.description: United States Chemical Weapons Convention Web Site: A resource of information about chemical weapons and the Chemical Weapons Convention (CWC) includes extensive material in HTML and PDF format, links to other sites related to the CWC, and access to the Web-DESI application used by U.S. chemical users to submit information in compliance with the CWC.
